00:11:45,706 --> 00:11:47,739
You ran out of time.
You got disqualified.

301
00:11:50,043 --> 00:11:53,745
But so what, that's not
going to happen this time.

302
00:11:55,215 --> 00:11:57,449
I'm going to be there and
