before registration closes.

307
00:12:06,927 --> 00:12:08,593
You're the best in town, pop.

308
00:12:09,496 --> 00:12:11,830
I mean, it says it right
there on your signs.

309
00:12:18,171 --> 00:12:19,571
- Okay.

310
00:12:19,606 --> 00:12:20,405
- Yeah?

311
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:21,406
- Let's do it.

312
00:12:21,441 --> 00:12:22,407
- Okay.

313
00:12:22,442 --> 00:12:23,274
- Okay.

