00:13:31,378 --> 00:13:33,611
- Ha ha. Not a chance.

338
00:13:35,081 --> 00:13:36,447
- Did you ask Santa
for what you wanted?

339
00:13:36,483 --> 00:13:39,951
- A secrets of the great
magicians magic set.

340
00:13:39,986 --> 00:13:43,488
- Oh, so you're into magic
these days. That's pretty cool.

341
00:13:43,523 --> 00:13:44,656
- Lean down, aunt grace.

342
00:13:44,691 --> 00:13:45,590
- Okay.

343
00:13:47,060 --> 00:13:48,393
What've we got here?

344
00:13:48,428 --> 00:13:51,596
Okay. Oh boy. Starting out good.

345
00:13:55,535 --> 00:13:59,470
Whoa! That is
incredible. Nicely done.

346
00:13:59,506 --> 00:14:01,806
Okay, now can you do that
with a chicken sandwich

347
00:14:01,842 --> 00:14:03,174
because I am starving.

348
00:14:03,210 --> 00:14:04,075
- I can't, aunt grace.

349
00:14:04,110 --> 00:14:05,810
- You let me down, kid.

350
00:14:05,846 --> 00:14:07,078
All right.

351
00:14:07,113 --> 00:14:08,546
Well, I'm going to
grab something to eat,

352
00:14:08,582 --> 00:14:10,548
but I'll meet you guys at
the bright nights booth?

