00:14:15,589 --> 00:14:16,855
about bright nights?

356
00:14:16,890 --> 00:14:19,324
- How do you think? I
appealed to his ego.

357
00:14:19,359 --> 00:14:21,860
He saw a bunch of people lining
up to see a house decorated

358
00:14:21,895 --> 00:14:23,862
by that new company, glowscapes.

359
00:14:23,897 --> 00:14:26,264
I think that really
lit a fire under him.

360
00:14:26,299 --> 00:14:27,498
- Nono can bring it.

361
00:14:27,534 --> 00:14:28,733
- Yes.

362
00:14:28,768 --> 00:14:30,535
- Let's hope that attention
to detail that makes him such

