00:14:32,572 --> 00:14:34,906
- If we get into
bright night finals,

365
00:14:34,941 --> 00:14:37,375
I'm telling you we can win it.

366
00:14:37,410 --> 00:14:40,378
- If, ifs and buts
were candy and nuts,

367
00:14:40,413 --> 00:14:42,580
what a merry
Christmas it would be.

368
00:14:47,554 --> 00:14:49,454
- Two pizzelles, please.

369
00:14:49,489 --> 00:14:51,723
- What he said. Thank you.

370
00:14:54,461 --> 00:14:57,962
And a half dozen
assorted, please.

371
00:14:57,998 --> 00:15:01,266
- That's a lot, uncle
tony. Not good for you.

372
00:15:01,301 --> 00:15:02,734
- Well, they're not for me.

373
00:15:03,670 --> 00:15:04,569
Thank you.

374
00:15:07,841 --> 00:15:08,740
Excuse me.

