00:15:12,612 --> 00:15:14,112
but I wanted to thank
you for the other day.

377
00:15:14,147 --> 00:15:16,447
- It wasn't anything really.

378
00:15:17,317 --> 00:15:19,417
- If you were your
dad and I was my dad,

379
00:15:19,452 --> 00:15:22,220
you would have just kept
driving, so it's not nothing.

380
00:15:22,255 --> 00:15:25,823
- Well, fortunately, we're
not our fathers. (laughs)

381
00:15:25,859 --> 00:15:28,726
and who is this young
man? Is this your son?

382
00:15:28,762 --> 00:15:31,296
- No, no, no, no. This
is my nephew, Dante.

