00:15:58,925 --> 00:16:00,825
- So where do you call home?

398
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:02,393
- Richmond, actually.

399
00:16:03,296 --> 00:16:06,831
- I just came back about
a year ago from Boston.

400
00:16:09,903 --> 00:16:12,971
- Grace will find out about
the stores eventually, dear.

401
00:16:13,006 --> 00:16:15,606
- I just don't want to
worry her unnecessarily.

402
00:16:15,642 --> 00:16:18,176
I got us into this
mess, I can get us out.

403
00:16:18,211 --> 00:16:19,143
- Mm hm.

404
00:16:21,014 --> 00:16:21,913
- Hello.

405
00:16:23,984 --> 00:16:25,116
- Your wade...

406
00:16:26,019 --> 00:16:28,353
Of glowscapes by wade?

407
00:16:28,388 --> 00:16:29,854
- Wade Edwards,
pleased to meet you.

408
00:16:29,889 --> 00:16:33,324
- (laughs) I'm Wendy ryerson
head of the committee.

409
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:35,793
My husband and I can't
pass by one of your houses

410
00:16:35,829 --> 00:16:37,295
without stopping.

411
00:16:37,330 --> 00:16:39,864
It's like 4th of
July in December.

412
00:16:41,201 --> 00:16:42,967
- I'm so glad it brings you joy.

413
00:16:44,237 --> 00:16:46,537
- We'll be reviewing
the applications and
the committee will

414
00:16:46,573 --> 00:16:49,407
reach out to the four
prelim qualifiers sometime

415
00:16:49,442 --> 00:16:51,309
in a day or so.

416
00:16:51,344 --> 00:16:54,545
Be sure to keep your
ringer on. (laughs)

417
00:16:57,050 --> 00:16:57,849
hi!

418
00:16:57,884 --> 00:16:59,584
- Hey.
- Hi.

419
00:16:59,619 --> 00:17:01,919
- Can't wait to see what
you Ryans have for us

