00:17:23,977 --> 00:17:25,910
- $50,000!

430
00:17:25,945 --> 00:17:27,512
- Whoa!
- You're kidding me?

431
00:17:27,547 --> 00:17:30,948
- Not a bad stocking
stuffer. Right? (laughs)

432
00:17:30,984 --> 00:17:31,949
well, good luck!

